NOTE ON FIFA-RELATED BRAND ASSETS

The FIFA 2026 logos and brand imagery present in `public/` are property of the
Fédération Internationale de Football Association (FIFA) and are NOT covered
by the MIT license above. They are included in this repository for personal
and educational use only.

If you fork this repository for any other purpose, you should strip or replace
those assets and the related visual styling (group colors, phase colors,
cerimonial gold/silver/bronze tokens) to avoid trademark issues.

The codebase itself, including the AI agent suite (`.claude/`), is yours to
use under the MIT terms.
